The paper discusses the concept of curriculum learning in the context of machine learning, specifically in the areas of linear regression and binary classification. This makes it likely to fall under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
